OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPoverty is Wales' major    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchallenge, warn officials  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Poverty in Wales is the "single major  
OL,6, challenge", an official report has     
OL,7, warned.                                
OL,9,FFigures suggest more than a third of   
OL,10,Fchildren in Wales are now classed as   
OL,11,Fliving in poverty, more than anywhere  
OL,12,Felse in the UK.                        
OL,14,FThe Audit Office has called for renewed
OL,15,Ffocus across every tier of government  
OL,16,Fin Wales to address the issue.         
OL,18,FIt includes a key recommendation for   
OL,19,Fnew a national strategy and targets to 
OL,20,Ftackle poverty.                        
